With this app you can create a list with all your favorite movies and TV shows.

this app is made with flask and you'll need to create a .env file with your keys :

MOVIE_DB_SEARCH_URL="https://api.themoviedb.org/3/search/movie"

Movies are order by the rating you give them
you can add, edit and delete every entry you make
you can add them with a rating and a review